channel.title: [HELP] One problem with moparscape server status
channel.description:
Hey, my name is Nick.
I recently have had trouble with the MoparScape server status. When I put my IP and click submit after filling out the form, it says "sorry, you only get to post one server.", Thing is, I don't have any servers on the status and it has been two days that it has been saying this to me.
A suggestion to this would be a button that shows what server you have added.
please help me, I need to post my server.
P.S. If this is the wrong section, please direct me to the right one being moparisthebest.com doesn't have anything about the mopar status, I figured this was the more relevant site to post on.
Thanks.

item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

Well, you must have posted it a couple days ago, then turned you server off. Your server must still be in the database. The only way you can fix this is to turn your server off until it’s off the list.
